{"tid":819616,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"山竹會帶來幾十米潮?【颶風威力】1.8米風暴潮破壞力如何？ 足以沖走汽車淹沒平房","createTime":"2018-09-15T03:07:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-15T03:07:40.000Z","uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8d9e5da55756197ed39ab410416da9d09f589a55","tid":819616,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T03:07:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180915/58680720\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180915%2F58680720&d=B3GW4%2BvoEe8pGhqZokSDYvjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=303764d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180915%2F58680720&h=35d22ffa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180915/58680720</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n颶風「弗洛倫斯」（Florence）迫近美國東部海岸，氣象部門預測會帶來暴雨，及高達1.8米（6呎）甚至3.3米（11呎）的風暴潮。究竟1.8米的風暴潮破壞力如何？氣象頻道網站（The Weather Channel）製作了模擬短片讓民眾有更深入的概念，場面觸目驚心。<br />\n頻道的颶風專家波斯特（Greg Poste）透過模擬短片講解颶風的威力，當風暴潮達0.9米（3呎），聽起來好像不太高，但實際已有危險，足以令人站不穩甚至跌倒；當風暴潮上升至1.8米（6呎），更足以沖走汽車，令汽車在水中飄流，更會淹沒大廈較低樓層；一旦風暴潮升到2.7米（9呎），更會淹沒平房。<br />\n當地氣象部門預測，「弗洛倫斯」除了導致風暴潮外，亦會帶來多達101厘米（1010毫米）的暴雨量，可能導致南卡羅來州及北卡羅來納州在美國時間周四晚上或周五發生山泥傾瀉。"},{"pid":"8c686842487d68b70322320658ff05d067026448","tid":819616,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T03:07:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}